      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_da5578ed6cfb92c79c921458959056c0">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Kingman Brewster, Jr., was inaugurated the seventeenth president of Yale University on 11 April 1964. The records document the planning and management of the inauguration and include press materials, such as clippings, releases, and the Yale Daily News special inauguration edition; invitations, tickets, and the ceremony program; congratulation messages; invitation and attendance lists; and records detailing ceremonial order and logistics. The records also include congratulation messages on Brewster's appointment as Yale University Provost in 1959.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
  
